text: Duygu Üçdağ (née Çetav, born June 7, 1988 in Istanbul) is a Circassian volleyball player. She played for Yeşilyurt İstanbul, Iller Bankasi Ankara, Halkbank, and PTT Spor Kulübü. == References == Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Istanbul Category:Turkish volleyball players
